sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Human
    participant Chrome as Chrome<br/>(user-launched w/ --remote-debugging-port)
    participant RealApp as Real ChatGPT<br/>(tab in Chrome)
    participant Replicata as replicata core<br/>(Node.js)
    participant Server as replicata HTTP server<br/>(127.0.0.1:3589)
    participant Renderer as user's renderer<br/>(localhost:5173)
    participant UI as replicata UI tab

    Note over Human,UI: Setup (once per session)
    Human->>Chrome: npm run chrome<br/>(launches Chrome w/ --remote-debugging-port=9222)
    Human->>RealApp: log into ChatGPT
    Replicata->>Chrome: chromium.connectOverCDP (npm run dev)
    Replicata->>RealApp: install passive fetch tap<br/>(addInitScript + evaluate)
    Replicata->>Renderer: install fetch redirect<br/>(endpoint routes → replicata server)
    Replicata->>UI: navigate to /ui (served by replicata)
    UI-->>Server: SSE /events (live state push)

    Note over Human,Renderer: Human-driven interaction
    Human->>RealApp: types prompt, submits
    RealApp->>RealApp: ChatGPT issues fetch('/backend-api/conversation')
    Note over RealApp: tap is transparent —<br/>real fetch executes normally

    Note over RealApp: response.body.tee() splits<br/>the stream into two readers
    RealApp->>RealApp: leg A → ChatGPT UI<br/>(normal render)
    RealApp-)Replicata: leg B → replicata observes<br/>via __replicataChunk(chunk)

    Replicata->>Replicata: StreamBuffer.addChunk()

    Note over Renderer,Server: Renderer consumes (after stream completes)
    Renderer->>Renderer: fetch('/api/chat')
    Renderer->>Server: (redirected) GET /stream/ep_xxx
    Note over Server: stream not complete yet → hold connection
    RealApp-)Replicata: __replicataStreamEnd(id)
    Replicata->>Server: markDone(id) → onStreamDone fires
    Server->>Renderer: replay chunks with original timing
    Server->>Server: connection closed after last chunk

    Note over Human,UI: Next message
    Renderer->>Server: fetch('/api/chat') again
    Server-->>Renderer: holds connection open<br/>(no unserved stream yet)
    Human->>RealApp: sends another message
    RealApp-)Replicata: new stream observed
    Note over Server: waits for completion
    RealApp-)Replicata: stream ends
    Server-)Renderer: replays the new stream
